This is a simple jQuery plugin to pre-fill an input element
with a specified value, which when the input fields is
selected, the pre-filled value will be hidden.

Usage:

<input type="text" value="" data-hint="Search..." class="dh" />

<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function() {
    $('input.dh').DataHint();
});
</script>
